### Test Promotion Filter API (GET với query parameters, response theo pattern Trip)

### 1. Filter tất cả promotions với phân trang mặc định (trang 1, 20 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter

### 2. Filter với phân trang tùy chỉnh (trang 2, 5 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?page=2&size=5

### 3. Filter theo status (chỉ active promotions)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?status=active

### 4. Filter theo type (chỉ coupon promotions)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?type=coupon

### 5. Filter theo khoảng discount (từ 10 đến 50)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?minDiscount=10&maxDiscount=50

### 6. Search theo code hoặc description
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=SUMMER

### 7. Filter theo khoảng thời gian (promotions bắt đầu từ hôm nay)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?startDate=2025-09-08

### 8. Filter combo: active coupon promotions với discount > 20%, trang 1, 3 items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?status=active&type=coupon&minDiscount=20&page=1&size=3

### 9. Search kết hợp filter: tìm "NEW" trong active promotions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=NEW&status=active

### 10. Filter theo khoảng thời gian kết thúc
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?endDate=2025-12-31

### 11. Filter đầy đủ với tất cả tham số
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=DISCOUNT&status=active&type=auto&minDiscount=15&maxDiscount=100&startDate=2025-09-01&endDate=2025-12-31&page=1&size=10

### 12. Test với auto promotions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?type=auto&status=active

### 13. Test với expired promotions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?status=expired